summary: SummaryL'OrÃ©al Paris' Infallible 24H Fresh Wear Foundation In A Powder covers like a liquid and mattifies like a powder with no cakey look.
details: DetailsBenefitsUp to 24hr matte finish & full coverage that stays fresh all dayLightweight formula that feels breathableAll day shine control with no transferWaterproof, heatproof & sweatproofSuitable for all skin types, oily & acne-prone skinItem 2575170How To UseApply to skin using the included sponge applicator. Sponge provides optimal product pickup and has a smooth surface for enhanced blendability. Use wet for full coverage or dry for medium, buildable coverage.For external use only. Do not use on damaged or broken skin. When using this product, keep out of eyes. Rinse with water to remove. Stop use and ask a doctor if rash occurs. Keep out of reach of children. reviews.headline: I keep going back
reviews.comments: It does stay all day on my mature skin and I try other products but keep coming back to this one. It is tried and true

reviews.headline: Great product butâ€¦
reviews.comments: I love the coverage, however, the powder breaks/ crack's easily it happens every time I use it for the first time.

reviews.headline: Damaged product
reviews.comments: This was the last compact in my shade and of course the product was shattered. Ulta employee wouldn't check the stock room and didn't offer a discount for damaged item.

reviews.headline: AMAZING BUT IT BREAKS
reviews.comments:
amazing powder. probably the best ive ever usedâ€¦ I want to keep buying it cause ive finally found a good one. 

*****BUT IT BREAKS. EASILY. *****

reviews.headline: Best Powder Foundation
reviews.comments: This is best powder foundation for a smooth flawless finish.  The only con is that it breaks easily:(

reviews.headline: Had to return for replacement
reviews.comments: ULTA failed to package properly so this item came  BROKEN!!!!  I would recommend the item but not for shipment.

reviews.headline: I liked it but unsatisfied with the quality
reviews.comments: I used it one day and loved it,  but next day when I opened it all the powder started falling out, it started with just one part but now all the powder base is complety "broken" I can use it but very carefully and unable to carry it with me :(

reviews.headline: Broken
reviews.comments: Dont order for shipment. Just received mine & powder all overbox. Ordered 2 due to a bogo deal. Both busted. Not at clise ulta stores so guess im driving 10 miles out of my way to get replacement tomorrow. This is the 4th time this has happened w/ pallettes over last few years. Figure this out ulta!!!!

reviews.headline: shattered and spilled everywhere
reviews.comments: I'm so disappointed. I was looking forward to having the matching powder and it came in completely busted up and shattered

reviews.headline: Good finishing powder
reviews.comments: I tried this for the summer as setting powder. It works well, stays on all day and I'm not completely oily/cakey after 10+ hours of wear.

reviews.headline: Used for less than a month and it is falling apart.
reviews.comments: I really like the powdered foundation and it was good in the beginning. Has a mice smell. Has mirror but i wish it came with a sponge to apply the foundation. It also started falling apart within a month and became loose powder at this point. I am a little disappointed about that becasue it works really well untill it started falling apart on me:(

reviews.headline: A favorite
reviews.comments: I'm dark skin with neutral undertones. Color match was great. Good coverage, goes on smooth. Doesn't cake or crease.

reviews.headline: Nice over tinted moisturizer
reviews.comments: Since my review a month ago, I started wearing a light amount of this powder foundation over tinted moisturizer. It really looks nice. It is not dry or flat looking at all. I use a fluffy, flatish blush brush to lightly powder my entire face.  My face has a nice glow. I recommend.

reviews.headline: Miracle worker!
reviews.comments:
Infallible 24hr is fabulous ðŸ‘Œ  takes 10 years of my face  
I LUV it!!!!!!

reviews.headline: Polka dot pores
reviews.comments: I tried using this over a mineral sunscreen and a chemical sunscreen. Both left dots of the powder foundation settle in my pores, making them more prominent. I had high hopes for this product after seeing reviews, but it didn't work for me.

reviews.headline: Good concealer
reviews.comments: I use this as concealer under my eyes, on my lids  and to cover dark spots over my light foundation. It works well and lasts all day.  I wouldn't care for it as foundation, but its good concealer. I have 125 Ivory Buff, but will get a lighter shade next time. But this shade is workable.

reviews.headline: Not for dry skin
reviews.comments: I had high hops for this as a quick solution to early mornings.  It was very chalky feeling on my skin.

reviews.headline: Nice Powder Foundation
reviews.comments: This is a great powder foundation for the price. Has a scent but nothing too overpowering. I hate scented makeup but this one isn't so bad.

reviews.headline: I will definitely buy this product
reviews.comments: I love this product it makes me feel confident cause I know it's going to last me all day.

reviews.headline: LOVEE!!
reviews.comments: I love this product. I love the way it covers spots I want it too, love the way it feels on my face not to heavy just light.
